{"tid":2337090,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良：如有官員嚴重抗疫疲勞「畀佢抖吓」","createTime":"2020-12-23T05:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T16:22:31.000Z","uid":5195,"like":23,"dislike":91,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"9364fcd2c946ac998359e566a199dd35a4444b3a","tid":2337090,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:22:09.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情近一年，香港爆發第4波疫情至今未受控。港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良今日在電台節目表示，政府應檢討指揮系統是否出問題，「如果有官員有嚴重抗疫疲勞，畀佢抖下」，指作指揮的官員能力要強，亦要夠高級，「愈高級愈好」。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良亦建議，政府現時發現一幢大廈內出現多宗確診，應立即要求全幢大廈強檢，「再過多兩日多幾宗個案再強檢就慢咗」，並命令未有結果前大廈須留家，若政府能加快檢測結果，找外判保安或警察守着大廈門口就可，才能夠中斷傳播鏈。"},{"pid":"2354d904ec5a7ea76e1dbc162f1a93343acccfd0","tid":2337090,"uid":77196,"like":154,"dislike":5,"score":149,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:24:53.000Z","msg":"吓，我都抗疫咗成年，邊個俾我抖吓？"},{"pid":"a389092ae18f5c4c997b3fc1abeb62a9424a4604","tid":2337090,"uid":28524,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:24:53.000Z","msg":"高級只係代表佢哋係收高人工嘅廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf353fa49fc146eea1645634ded25fdbcd2c98b","tid":2337090,"uid":24707,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:25:36.000Z","msg":"食屎啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c172433d6ab868eea76e07c38ece6907e64f7f","tid":2337090,"uid":11291,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:27:18.000Z","msg":"可唔可以畀鄭月娥收皮？"},{"pid":"d71deeadb34e70176faa721ed5e3c63051c43713","tid":2337090,"uid":136431,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"唞吓好 Rest in pieces<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f47c4c28b38f21f6774160b08ef222a4099a4a","tid":2337090,"uid":27530,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"佢意係叫唔掂既走，比其他有能力嘅人上場"},{"pid":"19fa3d25df498a9b92bd76d0c58d9d05ab375bad","tid":2337090,"uid":340088,"like":4,"dislike